       SAVE IN24, KOUNT, MKOUNT, INSEED
       INTEGER LUXLEV
       LOGICAL NOTYET
       DATA NOTYET, LUXLEV, IN24, KOUNT, MKOUNT /.TRUE., LXDFLT, 0,0,0/
